 Accept and Enter Site DeclineYou are about to leave the Vontobel Asset Management, Inc. website.  AgreeDeclineOur Process
HomeAbout UsOur ProcessOur Approach: Rigorous. Disciplined.
Time-tested.
We consistently apply the same disciplined approach across all strategies, regardless of the market environment.
1. Screen & Idea GenerationDOES THE BUSINESS PASS OUR HIGH HURDLE RATES?
We look for profitable and stable companies.
~50,000 stocks2. Analyze Past ResultsDO WE UNDERSTAND THE BUSINESS AND THE QUALITY OF ITS EARNINGS?
We look for companies that have generated predictable and sustainable earnings growth.
Investment universe of several hundred stocks3. Analyze Future OpportunitiesCAN THE BUSINESS REPLICATE AND EXCEED ITS PAST SUCCESS?
We look for high quality characteristics that will enable a company to maintain a high return on equity and moderate leverage.
Investment universe of several hundred stocks4. Determine a Sensible PriceIS THE COMPANY TRADING AT A SENSIBLE PRICE?
We look to buy and hold shares that are selling below our appraisal of their fundamental business value.
Investment universe of several hundred stocks5. Build Portfolio & Manage RiskARE WE SELECTING THE BEST NAMES AND WEIGHING THEM APPROPRIATELY?
We build concentrated portfolios using a common sense approach to risk diversification.
