									Vontobel Asset Management
								
									Swiss roots – global presence
								
									Vontobel Asset Management is a global, active, multi-boutique asset manager with Swiss roots and investment teams in Zurich, New York, Milan and London. Drawing on outstanding investment talent and a strong performance culture, each of our boutiques is driven by the aim of delivering a market leading offering in their respective asset classes.
								 
Learn more


































										Contact Us
									





Locations











									Social Media
								You can follow us on LinkedIn, Twitter and YouTube.
LinkedInTwitterYouTube



















									Investment Boutiques
								Each one of our boutiques is a specialised investment manager, with their own investment approach that is built to achieve outstanding and repeatable performance results in the asset class they cover.







Equities


Fixed Income


Multi Asset




Our two equity boutiques comprise of the Quality Growth Boutique based in New York and the Thematic Investing Boutique based in Zurich.


Actively managed fixed-income investment strategies from our Zurich based Fixed Income Boutique and London based TwentyFour Asset Management.


Our Multi Asset Class offering provides investors with an offering of various multi-asset class solutions including sustainable and quantitative investing.





