									Investment Themes
								Below you will find investment themes which we consider to be especially attractive. They provide a common thread running through our entire offering, and in our view have long-term relevance for the asset-management industry.















										Flexible Fixed Income
									
Many bond investors have not taken the necessary steps to address the ongoing challenge of a prolonged period of low interest rates.




Further information













										Spread Carry Run
									
There is always value in fixed income and in a world of near zero central bank rates, the corporate-credit market offers an enticing spread over government bonds.




Further information



































